<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <title>Privacy Policy — HealthyGrowth AI</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <style>
    .policy-content { max-width:480px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px 16px 80px; }
    .policy-hero { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a06,#070709); border:1px solid rgba(200,241,53,0.15); border-radius:20px; padding:24px 20px; margin-bottom:20px; text-align:center; }
    .policy-hero .icon { font-size:42px; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .policy-hero h1 { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:800; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c8f135,#a0e030); -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; background-clip:text; margin-bottom:6px; }
    .policy-hero p { font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); font-weight:500; }
    .policy-section { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; padding:18px; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .policy-section h2 { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:var(--lime); margin-bottom:10px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }
    .policy-section p, .policy-section li { font-size:13px; color:#b0b0c0; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .policy-section ul { padding-left:16px; margin:8px 0; }
    .policy-section li { margin-bottom:6px; }
    .bold { color:var(--text) !important; font-weight:600 !important; }
    .highlight-box { background:rgba(200,241,53,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(200,241,53,0.15); border-radius:10px; padding:12px 14px; margin:10px 0; }
    .highlight-box p { font-size:13px; color:var(--lime) !important; font-weight:600 !important; margin:0 !important; }
    .contact-card { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0e0818,#070709); border:1px solid rgba(155,93,229,0.2); border-radius:16px; padding:18px; margin-bottom:12px; text-align:center; }
    .contact-card h2 { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#c5a0f0; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .contact-card p { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:6px; }
    .contact-card a { color:var(--lime); text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; }
    .last-updated { text-align:center; font-size:11px; color:var(--muted2); padding:10px; }
    .back-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding:16px 18px; background:var(--bg); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50; }
    .back-header a { color:var(--lime); text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; }
    .back-header span { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); }
    a { color:var(--lime); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="back-header">
  <a href="index.html">← Back</a>
  <span>Privacy Policy</span>
</div>

<div class="policy-content">

  <div class="policy-hero">
    <div class="icon">🔒</div>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>HealthyGrowth AI · Effective Date: January 1, 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>👋 Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to HealthyGrowth AI ("the App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and being fully transparent about how your information is handled.</p>
    <p>By using HealthyGrowth AI, you agree to the terms described in this Privacy Policy. Please read it carefully.</p>
    <div class="highlight-box"><p>🌱 HealthyGrowth AI is designed with your privacy first. Most of your data never leaves your device.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>📋 Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><span class="bold">Data stored locally on your device only:</span></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name entered during onboarding</li>
      <li>Your selected goal and app preferences</li>
      <li>Daily tasks and plans you create</li>
      <li>Habits you track and their completion records</li>
      <li>Streak counts and history</li>
      <li>Night reflection entries and mood ratings</li>
      <li>Weekly progress scores</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="highlight-box"><p>✅ All of the above is stored only on your device. We do not collect, store, or have access to this data on any server.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>🤖 AI Coach & Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>When you use the AI Coach, your messages are sent through a secure Cloudflare Workers server to Groq's AI API to generate responses.</p>
    <p><span class="bold">What is sent to generate your response:</span></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your chat messages to the AI Coach</li>
      <li>Your first name, goal, and streak count for personalisation</li>
    </ul>
    <p><span class="bold">What is NOT stored:</span></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Conversations are not stored on our servers</li>
      <li>No history is retained after your session ends</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Groq's processing is subject to their Privacy Policy at <a href="https://groq.com/privacy">groq.com/privacy</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>📢 Advertising</h2>
    <p>HealthyGrowth AI displays ads provided by Google AdMob to support free access to the app. AdMob may collect and use data to serve personalised ads.</p>
    <p><span class="bold">AdMob may collect:</span></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Device identifiers such as Advertising ID</li>
      <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
      <li>App usage data for ad targeting</li>
      <li>Device type, OS version, and language settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can opt out of personalised ads by going to: <span class="bold">Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalisation</span> on your Android device.</p>
    <p>Google's full Privacy Policy: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">policies.google.com/privacy</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>🔑 App Permissions</h2>
    <p>HealthyGrowth AI requests only the following device permission:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><span class="bold">Internet access</span> — required for the AI Coach feature and displaying ads</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="highlight-box"><p>✅ We do not request access to your camera, microphone, contacts, location, files, or any other sensitive permissions.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>🛡️ Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take security seriously. Here is how we protect your information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>All AI Coach requests are routed through encrypted Cloudflare Workers — API keys are never exposed in the app</li>
      <li>All communication uses HTTPS encryption</li>
      <li>Your personal data stays on your device and is never transmitted to us</li>
      <li>We do not maintain any user accounts or databases containing your personal information</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>👶 Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>HealthyGrowth AI is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
    <p>If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has used this app, please contact us and we will take immediate steps to address any concerns.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>⚖️ Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have full control over your data at all times:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><span class="bold">Access:</span> All your data is visible within the app</li>
      <li><span class="bold">Delete:</span> Delete all your data anytime — go to Settings → Clear All Data</li>
      <li><span class="bold">Portability:</span> Your data lives on your device and is fully under your control</li>
      <li><span class="bold">Opt-out:</span> Opt out of personalised ads through your Android device settings</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h2>🔄 Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the effective date at the top of this page.</p>
    <p>Continued use of HealthyGrowth AI after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-card">
    <h2>📬 Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please reach out:</p>
    <p><span style="color:var(--text);font-weight:700;">HealthyGrowth AI</span></p>
    <p>📧 <a href="mailto:support@healthygrowthai.com">support@healthygrowthai.com</a></p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2);">We aim to respond to all privacy inquiries within 48 hours.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="last-updated">Last updated: January 1, 2026 · HealthyGrowth AI</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
